Package pl.ais.commons.domain.specification.simple

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AfterSpecification<C extends Comparable<? super C>>
    Specification implementation which is satisfied only if candidate is after predefined bound.
    BeforeSpecification<C extends Comparable<? super C>>
    Specification implementation which is satisfied only if candidate is before predefined bound.
    BlankSpecification
    Specification implementation which is satisfied only if character sequence is null, empty or holds whitespaces only.
    EmptySpecification<C>
    Specification implementation which is satisfied only if provided candidate is empty.
    FitIntoSpecification
    Specification implementation which is satisfied only if provided character sequence length is limited to predefined number of characters, or the character sequence is null.
    IsEqualSpecification<C>
    Specification implementation satisfied by candidates equal to some predefined value.
    RegexSpecification
    Specification implementation satisfied when candidate matches predefined regular expression.
    TrueSpecification<C>
    Specification implementation satisfied by any candidate.
